divs: Sighting DetailsI was at home watching tv. I went out side because there were jets flying low and it was strange because they seemed very low and I heard the dogs barking next door. When I first noticed it I thought it was an airplane with two binking lights. It blinked on and off and when it dissapered I thought the plane just turned its back side and I could no longer see the lights anymore.The second time I saw it after a minute I sat down again and the same lights were in the same spot again. then it dissapared . The lights looked very high in the sky orange and redish , I was kinda of supprised and I then believed that mabey I saw a ufo.
